  "Say": {
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "The daimyo was good enough to provide me a training ground, despite their feeble resources, but my powers still elude me. The realities of this new world are maddening. Will I ever find my strength?"
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "I must collect my thoughts. And perhaps find a good daikon-infused hot pot."
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirType": "sub"
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "My first mission must be to regain my power. Only then will I be of use to the alliance."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "Only then will I be able to save the princess. I cannot imagine the fear and strain she must be experiencing, but I will revisit it upon Nobunaga tenfold."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "Before any of that, I must locate the scoundrel Oda Nobunaga. The people of this strange land can not possibly be prepared for the evil he will bring."
      },
      "3": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "The road ahead is long and winding, frought with peril, as it must be. I will free Momijigaoka of its troubles, then I will deal with the demon king."
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirType": "sub"
      }
    }
